I co-own Louder Than Eleven (www.lt11.com), an adventure media house based in Boulder, Colorado.  We produce captivating film and photo content in challenging environments around the world. I thrive on telling stories that speak to the core of the outdoor community by capturing the raw passion of people doing what they love.

If you enjoy my images and videos, subscribe to my channel and give me a follow on Instagram(@jonglassberg).

data.name: Leavenworth Bouldering
data.description:
We spent just over a week climbing in the Leavenworth, Washington area, most of it bouldering.  Leavenworth is a pretty awesome bouldering destination, with a high percentage of excellent problems.

The town itself is also quite interesting, themed in a Bavarian style.  As we were there towards the end of September, Oktoberfest celebrations were just getting into full swing.

Problems included are:
The Break V2
420 Slab V0
Sunny and Steep V2
The Real Thing V4
The Pocket V4
Drugstore Cowboy V3
